text: Angga Saputro (born November 30, 1993) is an Indonesian professional footballer who plays as a goalkeeper for Liga 1 club Persebaya Surabaya. ==Career== He made his professional debut in the Liga 1 on April 16, 2017.Soccerway Profile ==Honours== ===Club=== Persebaya Surabaya * East Java Governor Cup: 2020 ==References== ==External links== * Category:TIRA-Persikabo Category:1993 births Category:Indonesian footballers Category:Association football goalkeepers Category:Liga 1 (Indonesia) players Category:Living people Category:Persikabo 1973 players Category:Madura United F.C. players
